<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR" data-theme="light">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pagamento Pendente - HocketZap</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@2.51.5/dist/full.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/your-fontawesome-kit.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        }
        .animate-pulse {
            animation: pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: .5; }
        }
        .animate-bounce {
            animation: bounce 1s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(-25%); animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.8, 0, 1, 1); }
            50% { transform: translateY(0); animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden transform transition-all hover:scale-105 duration-300">
        <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-indigo-600 text-white text-center relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full">
                    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="10" fill="#fff"/>
                    <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="5" fill="#fff"/>
                    <circle cx="70" cy="70" r="8" fill="#fff"/>
                    <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="12" fill="#fff"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <i class="fas fa-clock text-6xl mb-4 animate-pulse"></i>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Pagamento Pendente</h1>
            <p class="text-lg opacity-75">Estamos processando sua transação</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8">
            <div class="alert bg-yellow-100 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 text-yellow-700 p-4 mb-6" role="alert">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-2xl mr-4"></i>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Seu pagamento está em análise pelo Mercado Pago.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                Obrigado por escolher o HocketZap! Seu pagamento está sendo processado e isso geralmente leva apenas alguns minutos. Em casos excepcionais, pode demorar até 48 horas.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="bg-green-500 rounded-full p-2 mr-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-white"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-lg">Pedido recebido com sucesso</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="bg-blue-500 rounded-full p-2 mr-4 animate-spin">
                        <i class="fas fa-spinner text-white"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-lg">Aguardando confirmação do pagamento</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400">
                    <div class="border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-full p-2 mr-4">
                        <i class="far fa-circle"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-lg">Ativação do plano</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-gray-50 border-t">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-purple-600">Próximos passos:</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope text-purple-500 mr-3"></i>
                    <span>Verifique seu e-mail para atualizações</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt text-purple-500 mr-3"></i>
                    <span>Cheque o status no app do Mercado Pago</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock text-purple-500 mr-3"></i>
                    <span>Aguarde a confirmação automática</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-indigo-600">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-lg btn-white hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg">
                Voltar para o Dashboard
            </a>
            <p class="mt-6 text-white opacity-75">
                Dúvidas? <a href="/contato" class="font-bold hover:underline">Entre em contato conosco</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fixed bottom-4 right-4 animate-bounce">
        <a href="#" class="bg-white text-purple-600 rounded-full p-4 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <i class="fas fa-question-circle text-2xl"></i>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>